        "info": "This API demonstrates all security layers working together on EVERY request:\n\n**Request Flow:**\n1. HTTPS/TLS (Port 3443) - encrypted transport\n2. OAuth2/JWT validation via Keycloak\n3. OPA policy authorization check\n4. SQL Server query execution\n\n**Key Settings:**\n- `autoGenerateSql: true` - framework generates SQL\n- `useFlowOutput: false` - no custom handlers needed\n- `crudOperation: list|get|create|update|delete`\n\nNo mock data - all queries hit the real database!",
